<section class="page-mast wrap center reveal">
  <span class="eyebrow"><span data-ar>كالابريز</span><span data-en>Calapres</span></span>
  <h1 class="display d-1"><span data-ar>الدار تفتح قريبًا</span><span data-en>The maison opens soon</span></h1>
  <p class="lede"><span data-ar>اترك بريدك لنخبرك عند فتح التجربة.</span><span data-en>Leave your email and we will let you know when the experience opens.</span></p>
</section>

<section class="section wrap account-narrow">
  <div class="account-card">
    {%- form 'storefront_password', class: 'contact-form' -%}
      {%- if form.errors -%}<div class="form-error">{{ form.errors | default_errors }}</div>{%- endif -%}
      <label>
        <span><span data-ar>كلمة المرور</span><span data-en>Password</span></span>
        <input type="password" name="password" autocomplete="current-password" required>
      </label>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit"><span data-ar>دخول</span><span data-en>Enter</span></button>
    {%- endform -%}
  </div>
</section>
